        @Nullable
public com.mojang.bridge.game.GameSession getCurrentSession()
        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: com.mojang.bridge.game.RunningGame
        Gets the current game session.

        A "game session" is defined as an actual gameplay session, such as playing in singleplayer, not the client's own session. See the documentation for GameSession for more.

        This method may return a "snapshot" of the current session information, and may not be kept up to date. Launchers should call this method to get a fresh GameSession whenever required.
